{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
        "name": "Airport API (Symfony)",
        "description": "Full CRUD API for managing airport planes.\n\n## Data Model: Plane\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| id | integer | auto | Unique identifier (auto-generated) |\n| model | string | yes | Aircraft model name |\n| airline | string | yes | Airline company name |\n\n## Status Codes\n- `200` OK — request successful\n- `201` Created — resource created\n- `400` Bad Request — invalid JSON or missing fields\n- `404` Not Found — resource does not exist\n- `500` Internal Server Error — unexpected server error\n\n## Seed Data (in-memory)\nThe API starts with 4 pre-loaded planes:\n- ID 1: Boeing 747 — Ukraine International\n- ID 2: Airbus A320 — Wizz Air\n- ID 3: Antonov 225 — Antonov Dream Airlines\n- ID 4: Antonov 124 — Antonov Dream Airlines\n\n⚠️ Data is stored in-memory and resets on server restart.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:8000",
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Base URL for Symfony server (symfony serve or php -S localhost:8000/public)"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Planes",
            "description": "CRUD operations for airplane records",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "List all planes",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/planes",
                            "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                            "path": ["api", "planes"]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns an array of all planes in the system.\n\n**No parameters required.**\n\n### Response 200 OK\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": [\n    { \"id\": 1, \"model\": \"Boeing 747\", \"airline\": \"Ukraine International\" },\n    { \"id\": 2, \"model\": \"Airbus A320\", \"airline\": \"Wizz Air\" },\n    { \"id\": 3, \"model\": \"Antonov 225\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" },\n    { \"id\": 4, \"model\": \"Antonov 124\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" }\n  ]\n}\n```"
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "name": "200 OK — All planes returned",
                            "status": "OK",
                            "code": 200,
                            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                            "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
                            "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": [\n    { \"id\": 1, \"model\": \"Boeing 747\", \"airline\": \"Ukraine International\" },\n    { \"id\": 2, \"model\": \"Airbus A320\", \"airline\": \"Wizz Air\" },\n    { \"id\": 3, \"model\": \"Antonov 225\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" },\n    { \"id\": 4, \"model\": \"Antonov 124\", \"airline\": \"Antonov Dream Airlines\" }\n  ]\n}"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "name": "Create a new plane",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json",
                                "type": "text"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"model\": \"Boeing 737-800\",\n    \"airline\": \"Ryanair\"\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": { "language": "json" }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/planes",
                            "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                            "path": ["api", "planes"]
                        },
                        "description": "Creates a new plane record. Both `model` and `airline` are required and must be non-empty strings.\n\nThe `id` is auto-generated as `count(planes) + 1`.\n\n### Request Body\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"Boeing 737-800\",   // required\n  \"airline\": \"Ryanair\"         // required\n}\n```\n\n### Response 201 Created\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 5,\n  \"model\": \"Boeing 737-800\",\n  \"airline\": \"Ryanair\"\n}\n```\n\n### Response 400 — Invalid JSON\n```json\n{ \"error\": \"Invalid JSON format\" }\n```\n\n### Response 400 — Missing fields\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": \"Validation failed\",\n  \"details\": \"Fields \\\"model\\\" and \\\"airline\\\" are required\"\n}\n```\n\n### Response 500 — Server error\n```json\n{ \"error\": \"Server error\" }\n```"
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "name": "201 Created — Plane created successfully",
                            "status": "Created",
                            "code": 201,
                            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                            "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
                            "originalRequest": {
                                "method": "POST",
                                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                                "body": {
                                    "mode": "raw",
                                    "raw": "{\n    \"model\": \"Boeing 737-800\",\n    \"airline\": \"Ryanair\"\n}"
                                },
                                "url": {
                                    "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/planes",
