                        "description": "Permanently removes a plane record from the system. This action is irreversible.\n\n⚠️ Current implementation does not persist deletion (in-memory only).\n\n### Path Parameter\n| Name | Type | Required | Description |\n|------|------|----------|-------------|\n| id | integer | yes | ID of the plane to delete |\n\n### Response 200 OK\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Plane 2 has been deleted\"\n}\n```\n\n### Response 404 Not Found\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": \"Plane not found\"\n}\n```"
                    },
